            "headline": "Crombie REIT reports strong Q4 2024 results: 96.8% occupancy, $133,000 acquisition, $6,000 proceeds, $7,067 investment. 189.6% increase in operating income. FFO per Unit up 6.7% and AFFO per Unit up 7.7%.",
